#. module: newsassistant_blog
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:newsassistant_blog.res_config_settings_view_form_newsassistant_blog
msgid ""
"Write a teaser for this news article following these guidelines:\n"
"\n"
"- Length: 2-3 sentences (max 280 characters)\n"
"- Tone: Professional but accessible, informative\n"
"- Structure: Start with the key news, then why it matters\n"
"- Language: Use the same language as the original article\n"
"- Style: Neutral, factual, no clickbait or sensationalism\n"
"- Goal: Help readers quickly decide if they want to read the full article"
msgstr ""

#. module: newsassistant_blog
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:newsassistant_blog.res_config_settings_view_form_newsassistant_blog
msgid ""
"You are curating a newsfeed for Swiss social sector professionals.\n"
"\n"
"HIGHLY RELEVANT (auto-publish):\n"
"- Policy changes affecting social institutions in Switzerland\n"
"- Research findings on disability, integration, poverty, or social work\n"
"- Funding announcements for social projects\n"
"- Legal changes impacting NGOs or social services\n"
"\n"
"MAYBE RELEVANT (needs human review):\n"
"- General political news that might affect the social sector\n"
"- Events and conferences in the social field\n"
"- News from neighboring countries with Swiss implications\n"
"\n"
"NOT RELEVANT (discard):\n"
"- Entertainment, sports, lifestyle news\n"
"- News from other countries without Swiss connection\n"
"- Commercial press releases unrelated to social sector\n"
"- Duplicate or very similar content to recent articles"
msgstr ""

